[h1]Vigil at the Holy Site[/h1]

Devote yourself to your faith, and offer up a captive to seal the rite.

[h2]What it does[/h2]
Adds a once-per-game player decision. Sacrifice a captive at the holy place; receive 10,000 piety. The flavor text adapts to the ruler's faith family: Norse, Christian, Islamic, Tengri, or generic.

[list]
[*] Requires at least one prisoner.
[*] One use per save.
[*] Player-only.
[/list]

[h2]Compatibility[/h2]
[b]CK3 1.19.[/b] No vanilla file edits.
